title: Start
body:
Jenny: Hey, a cute cat!

		Jenny: Can I play with the cat for while?

title: DontPlayWithCat
body: Jenny:I am sorry kitty! Grandma is hungry, I must go now.

title: PlayWithCat
body: Oh no! The food is ruined by the kitty!
